  <summary>2/8/2011--Introduced.
Stands with the people of Colombia as they face the devastating consequences from floods. Urges the renewal of the temporary extension of the Andean Trade Promotion and Drug Eradication Act (ATPDEA). Calls on the President to engage in a relationship with Colombia, a long-standing democratic U.S. ally, that promotes economic growth and reinforces the fight against drug trafficking.</summary>
